	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you're using a 27C080, then SMB 2J should fit along with the other stuff fsince the PRG is 64 kB &amp; the CHR is 16 kB, and you have 128 kB left on each chip.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


